## 8. Scaling Path

### Phase 1 (<50k matches)

* Full replay fine
* Serverless OK

### Phase 2 (50k–500k matches)

* Chunked replay
* Possibly queue-based recompute

### Phase 3 (500k+ matches)

* Incremental rating engine
* Partitioned rating pools
* Background worker architecture

